1
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,340
[LUFFY groans]

2
00:01:51,340 --> 00:01:53,720
[LUFFY]
I'm so hungry.

3
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:56,100
[ZORO]
When the hell are we
gonna reach land anyway?

4
00:01:56,100 --> 00:01:57,100
[LUFFY]
Who knows?

5
00:01:57,100 --> 00:02:00,730
We're just sailin' on the wind and
the waves, going where they take us.

6
00:02:00,730 --> 00:02:01,770
[ZORO grunts]

7
00:02:01,770 --> 00:02:04,650
Don't you find it dumb that someone
trying to be King of the Pirates

8
00:02:04,650 --> 00:02:06,980
doesn't have a single
navigational skill?!

9
00:02:06,980 --> 00:02:08,360
Not really...

10
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,360
I just drift around...

11
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:14,110
What about you, aren't you some
famous bounty hunter who sailed the seas?

12
00:02:14,110 --> 00:02:17,990
I don't have any recollection
of ever calling myself a bounty hunter.

13
00:02:17,990 --> 00:02:19,240
[ZORO sighs]

14
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:22,330
I set out onto the open sea
in search of just one man,

15
00:02:22,330 --> 00:02:24,540
but then I couldn't
get back to my village.

16
00:02:25,210 --> 00:02:28,800
By that point, I had no choice but to
go after pirate ships to earn a living.

17
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,800
Oh, I see. So you're just lost.

18
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,840
Hey, don't put it like that!

19
00:02:31,300 --> 00:02:32,840
[LUFFY grunts]

20
00:02:38,930 --> 00:02:40,970
[HENCHMAN A chuckles]
Another big haul today!

21
00:02:40,970 --> 00:02:42,100
That's two in a row!

22
00:02:42,100 --> 00:02:45,140
[HENCHMAN B]
All of this should keep Buggy
from getting too mad at us.

23
00:02:45,140 --> 00:02:45,940
[HENCHMAN C]
Hey..

24
00:02:45,940 --> 00:02:48,230
What's with that boat out there?

25
00:02:48,230 --> 00:02:49,020
[HENCHMEN]
Huh?

26
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:53,820
We should check it out.

27
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,670
Oh... It's a lady.

28
00:03:08,670 --> 00:03:09,670
[HENCHMAN A chuckles]

29
00:03:09,670 --> 00:03:11,500
Hey, wake up little girl.

30
00:03:13,510 --> 00:03:14,260
Uh.

31
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:17,050
Please tell me I'm not
dreaming this time...

32
00:03:17,050 --> 00:03:20,220
Finding help out here
in the middle of nowhere...

33
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:23,310
If you're real, then please,
could you get me some water?

34
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:25,440
I'm so thirsty...

35
00:03:25,810 --> 00:03:28,520
I'll give you as much jewelry
and valuables as you like,

36
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,650
if you could just
give me one little drink.

37
00:03:30,650 --> 00:03:32,860
No sweat. We'll help ya.

38
00:03:32,860 --> 00:03:36,280
But not until we see what kinda
treasure you're holding on to.

39
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,610
[HENCHMAN B]
Yeah, don't mind us.

40
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:39,490
[HENCHMAN C chuckling]

41
00:03:37,610 --> 00:03:38,990
We'll just be a minute.

42
00:03:38,990 --> 00:03:39,780
[GIRL groans]

43
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:43,200
[HENCHMAN A]
Can't get the damn thing open!

44
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:44,700
Uh. Hold up, here we go.

45
00:03:46,290 --> 00:03:48,000
[HENCHMEN scream]

46
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,170
[GIRL laughing]

47
00:03:50,170 --> 00:03:52,420
If you want, you can
keep the whole thing!

48
00:03:52,420 --> 00:03:53,630
It's not my style.

49
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:57,220
[energetic music]

50
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:54,760
[HENCHMEN scream]

51
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,010
But that's our boat!

52
00:03:56,010 --> 00:03:57,220
You tricked us!

53
00:03:58,930 --> 00:04:02,970
From the look of those clouds moving in
from the south, I'd say a cold front's coming.

54
00:04:03,810 --> 00:04:07,940
So you can probably expect strong winds
and squalls any time now, really.

55
00:04:07,940 --> 00:04:11,980
Also, in that small boat,
you run a bit of a chance of capsizing.

56
00:04:12,940 --> 00:04:13,610
[HENCHMEN gasp]

57
00:04:16,860 --> 00:04:21,070
[HENCHMEN screaming]

58
00:04:21,070 --> 00:04:22,280
[GIRL]
Bingo!

59
00:04:23,410 --> 00:04:24,240
See ya!

60
00:04:24,990 --> 00:04:27,750
I'll just take whatever
treasure you guys got here!

61
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:29,750
[HENCHMAN A]
Get back here, you bitch!

62
00:04:29,750 --> 00:04:31,630
[HENCHMAN B gurgling]
We'll get you for this!

63
00:04:32,380 --> 00:04:35,800
[ZORO]
Uh. I am so hungry. It's killing me!

64
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,340
[LUFFY]
Hm?

65
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,760
[ZORO]
Hey, look, a bird.

66
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:41,390
I know! Let's eat it!

67
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,390
Huh? How do we catch it?

68
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:44,680
[LUFFY]
Leave that to me!

69
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,600
Gum-Gum...

70
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,060
Rocket!

71
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:51,730
Makes sense...

72
00:04:52,060 --> 00:04:53,310
[LUFFY yelps]

73
00:04:53,900 --> 00:04:55,020
[ZORO]
Hm?

74
00:04:55,650 --> 00:04:57,990
[LUFFY groaning]

75
00:04:57,990 --> 00:05:00,150
[energetic music]

76
00:04:58,320 --> 00:05:00,150
[LUFFY screaming]

77
00:05:00,150 --> 00:05:01,410
Help me!

78
00:05:01,410 --> 00:05:03,950
You moron! What the
hell's going on now?!

79
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:10,710
[HENCHMAN A gasps]
Hey, you there! Stop!

80
00:05:10,710 --> 00:05:13,460
Please! Men overboard!
Stop! Men overboard!

81
00:05:13,460 --> 00:05:16,750
I can't believe I find
ship-wreckers at a time like this!

82
00:05:16,750 --> 00:05:18,970
I can't stop, you're just
gonna have to jump in!

83
00:05:19,340 --> 00:05:20,680
[HENCHMEN]
What?!

84
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:23,430
[HENCHMEN screaming]

85
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:25,300
I'm actually impressed
you made it onboard.

86
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:26,760
[HENCHMEN]
Are you trying to kill us?!

87
00:05:27,140 --> 00:05:29,270
[HENCHMAN A]
Stop the boat now!

88
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:33,020
The three of us are members
of Buggy the Clown's pirate crew.

89
00:05:33,020 --> 00:05:34,610
This boat is ours now!

90
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,270
Huh?

91
00:05:37,110 --> 00:05:39,070
[HENCHMAN A laughing]

92
00:05:37,110 --> 00:05:43,030
[HENCHMAN B & C laughing]

93
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:39,610
I'm sorry...

94
00:05:39,610 --> 00:05:43,030
We had no idea you were the
famous Pirate Hunter Zoro! [chuckle]

95
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,240
[HENCHMEN]
Please forgive us!

96
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:48,370
[ZORO]
Thanks to you three idiots,
I lost sight of my friend.

97
00:05:48,370 --> 00:05:50,120
So just keep paddling.

98
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,210
[HENCHMEN]
Yes, sir!

99
00:05:51,210 --> 00:05:52,580
Knowing Luffy...

100
00:05:52,580 --> 00:05:55,590
he'll probably pull off
something once he spots land.

101
00:05:56,840 --> 00:06:00,590
[HENCHMAN B]
So, any ideas about what we do now?

102
00:06:00,590 --> 00:06:01,800
[HENCHMAN C]
Good question.

103
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:06,760
If Captain Buggy finds out a girl stole
our boat and our treasure, we're history.

104
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:07,810
[HENCHMAN A]
I know...

105
00:06:07,810 --> 00:06:10,020
[ZORO]
Huh? So who is this Buggy guy?

106
00:06:10,020 --> 00:06:13,270
[HENCHMAN A]
Uh... You've never heard
of Buggy the Clown?!

107
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:14,600
[ZORO]
Nope.

108
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:17,610
He's the ruthless captain
of our pirate ship.

109
00:06:17,610 --> 00:06:19,480
And he's eaten one of the Devil Fruits!

110
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:24,360
But above everything else,
he is a one truly terrifying man.

111
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:44,380
[GIRL]
Yes, I've finally got it!

112
00:06:44,380 --> 00:06:46,060
Hey girl, get back here!

113
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:48,640
You better give us
that map back or else!

114
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,640
[HENCHMAN X] We just stole
that chart of the Grand Line!

115
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,680
It belongs to us!

116
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,980
Dammit!

117
00:06:53,980 --> 00:06:56,480
If we don't get that thing back,
then we're as good as dead!

118
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:59,110
We'll be killed by one of
the Captain's cannonballs!

119
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:05,240
[HENCHMAN X]
Captain Buggy!

120
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:07,450
I've spotted something high
in the sky above the port.

121
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,620
[BUGGY]
Well, shoot it down!

122
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,250
What's that?

123
00:07:27,470 --> 00:07:28,930
What... was that?!

124
00:07:28,930 --> 00:07:30,550
What the hell...?

125
00:07:30,550 --> 00:07:32,140
A guy fell from the sky.

126
00:07:32,890 --> 00:07:33,640
[LUFFY]
Dammit...

127
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:36,730
Why were there
cannonballs flying at me?

128
00:07:41,860 --> 00:07:43,440
[LUFFY]
At least I'm safe now.

129
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,620
And...

130
00:07:44,620 --> 00:07:46,360
what just happened to me
was awesome.

131
00:07:50,410 --> 00:07:51,740
Geez...

132
00:07:51,740 --> 00:07:54,410
[LUFFY]
I'm so hungry.

133
00:07:51,910 --> 00:07:53,290
Oh, hey, boss!

134
00:07:53,290 --> 00:07:55,040
Thanks for coming to save me!

135
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,620
Huh?

136
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,830
Who're you?

137
00:08:00,210 --> 00:08:01,710
[GIRL]
They're all yours now, boss.

138
00:08:01,710 --> 00:08:02,670
Have fun!

139
00:08:05,550 --> 00:08:06,960
[HENCHMAN X]
Hey! That girl's getting away!

140
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:09,050
[HENCHMAN X] That's okay.
We've got her boss now.

141
00:08:09,050 --> 00:08:10,930
[HENCHMAN X]
You're in trouble, kid.

142
00:08:10,930 --> 00:08:13,430
You should have let
your crony fend for herself.

143
00:08:13,430 --> 00:08:15,930
You guys know of anywhere
good to eat around here?

144
00:08:15,930 --> 00:08:17,890
Food's the least of
your worries now!

145
00:08:17,890 --> 00:08:19,060
[gasps]

146
00:08:27,860 --> 00:08:30,030
You better keep your
hands off my hat!

147
00:08:30,030 --> 00:08:31,780
[BOTH]
You bastard!

148
00:08:31,780 --> 00:08:33,910
I wonder if they've
killed that poor guy yet.

149
00:08:34,870 --> 00:08:38,330
[LUFFY]
Gum-Gum Pistol!

150
00:08:43,670 --> 00:08:45,380
[GIRL]
Wow.

151
00:08:45,380 --> 00:08:47,380
You're really strong!

152
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:48,590
Huh?

153
00:08:50,260 --> 00:08:53,350
Even though both of them had sabers,
you beat them barehanded.

154
00:08:53,350 --> 00:08:55,140
[LUFFY]
Hey! You're the girl who set me up.

155
00:08:55,140 --> 00:08:56,270
Who are you?

156
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:59,390
I'm a talented thief
who steals strictly from pirates.

157
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:00,520
The name's Nami.

158
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:02,440
Hey... Wanna team up with me?

159
00:09:02,900 --> 00:09:05,900
Um, thanks anyway, lady,
but I think I'll pass.

160
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:06,780
[NAMI stammers]

161
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:08,190
Hold on...!

162
00:09:09,650 --> 00:09:11,360
[NAMI]
At least think about it first.

163
00:09:13,450 --> 00:09:16,620
[BUGGY]
You're telling me they
still haven't caught the thief?

164
00:09:16,620 --> 00:09:17,540
[HENCHMAN X]
Uh...

165
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:18,540
Not yet...

166
00:09:18,540 --> 00:09:19,660
But...

167
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:21,120
But they should be in pursuit...

168
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:23,170
right now, Captain... Sir.

169
00:09:24,170 --> 00:09:28,960
Now explain to me, how in the world did she
manage to get her hands on that chart, huh?!

170
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,130
[whimpering]

171
00:09:30,130 --> 00:09:33,970
If we're preparing to enter
the Grand Line, and go on a rampage,

172
00:09:33,970 --> 00:09:36,010
then why wasn't the chart
properly guarded?!

173
00:09:36,010 --> 00:09:37,390
I-I don't know, sir...

174
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:40,230
The map was just sitting out,
plain as the nose on your face.

175
00:09:40,230 --> 00:09:42,020
[BUGGY snorts]
What did you say?!

176
00:09:42,020 --> 00:09:44,650
I-I mean it was easy for
her to find and take it!

177
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:47,860
[BUGGY]
Did you say something
about my nose?!

178
00:09:47,860 --> 00:09:49,110
So!

179
00:09:49,110 --> 00:09:51,860
Are you trying to tell me
you find my nose funny?

180
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:54,030
Is my nose amusing?

181
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:55,830
No, sir, you've misunderstood!

182
00:09:55,830 --> 00:09:58,290
Oh, no, you were quite clear!

183
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,280
[HENCHMAN X whimpering]

184
00:10:01,250 --> 00:10:02,120
[HENCHMAN X]
Help me...

185
00:10:08,170 --> 00:10:09,550
This isn't good...

186
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:11,880
He's... gonna use the devil fruit power!

187
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,580
[BUGGY growls] [whimpering]

188
00:10:18,140 --> 00:10:19,810
Tell me, who am I?!

189
00:10:20,220 --> 00:10:21,560
[HENCHMAN X choking]

190
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:23,100
Captain...

191
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,770
Buggy...

192
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:30,730
And what happens
if someone defies me?

193
00:10:30,730 --> 00:10:37,660
Flashy... death... awaits... them...

194
00:10:37,660 --> 00:10:41,540
Please... forgive me!

195
00:10:43,370 --> 00:10:45,120
[BUGGY]
Quit your groveling.

196
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:48,170
I'll overlook your slip-up
and forgive you this time.

197
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:50,750
But you better get that chart back.

198
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:53,510
Don't screw up again... Or else.

199
00:10:53,510 --> 00:10:55,680
[HENCHMEN]
Yes, Captain Buggy!

200
00:11:01,310 --> 00:11:02,270
Yum.

201
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:04,770
So, do you live in this
big house all by yourself?

202
00:11:04,770 --> 00:11:07,860
This isn't my house, I'm just
staying here for the time being.

203
00:11:08,270 --> 00:11:11,190
Everyone's left this town
because of Captain Buggy.

204
00:11:11,190 --> 00:11:12,860
[LUFFY]
So you're just a petty thief.

205
00:11:12,860 --> 00:11:14,070
[NAMI]
How rude!

206
00:11:14,070 --> 00:11:17,320
I only steal from people
who deserve it: pirates.

207
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:20,530
So don't compare me
to some scumbag, petty thief.

208
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:23,040
A thief's a thief,
as far as I'm concerned.

209
00:11:24,250 --> 00:11:29,040
My goal is to earn a hundred million berries,
no matter how hard it is, or how long it takes.

210
00:11:29,380 --> 00:11:30,250
[LUFFY]
Hm.

211
00:11:30,250 --> 00:11:32,630
What do you need
so many berries for anyway?

212
00:11:32,630 --> 00:11:34,220
[NAMI]
It's a secret.

213
00:11:34,220 --> 00:11:36,220
But with this chart of the Grand Line...

214
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:39,720
the hundred million is
now a definite possibility.

215
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:41,350
A chart.

216
00:11:41,350 --> 00:11:42,890
So you must be a navigator.

217
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:46,520
I'm the most skilled navigator
you're ever likely to meet.

218
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:49,100
Oh, wow. That's perfect!

219
00:11:49,100 --> 00:11:52,440
Then how about you join my crew?
I've been looking to recruit a navigator.

220
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,440
Really?

221
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:53,940
Sure!

222
00:11:53,940 --> 00:11:55,900
You can be our newest crew member!

223
00:11:56,570 --> 00:11:57,400
No!

224
00:11:59,530 --> 00:12:01,530
I suppose this means you're a pirate.

225
00:12:01,530 --> 00:12:02,120
Yeah.

226
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,700
I made a solemn promise.

227
00:12:03,700 --> 00:12:06,410
I promised the guy who gave me
this hat that I'd form a crew,

228
00:12:06,410 --> 00:12:08,210
and become the greatest pirate ever.

229
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:12,000
There's nothing in this world
that I despise more than pirates!

230
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,960
I only like money and tangerines!

231
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,130
[LUFFY]
Come on.

232
00:12:15,130 --> 00:12:16,130
Be our navigator.

233
00:12:16,130 --> 00:12:17,420
I said no!

234
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:19,510
Your loss.

235
00:12:21,050 --> 00:12:22,720
[HENCHMAN X]
Did you find her or what?!

236
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,520
[HENCHMAN X]
No! I can't find her anywhere!

237
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:25,980
[HENCHMAN X]
Where could she be hiding?

238
00:12:25,980 --> 00:12:29,810
[HENCHMAN X]
I don't know, but we're gonna be
in big trouble if we don't get that chart back.

239
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:32,900
[NAMI]
I gotta do something about them.

240
00:12:33,020 --> 00:12:34,180
[chuckles]

241
00:12:34,230 --> 00:12:38,700
I guess I might consider joining you,
but only if you'll agree to certain conditions.

242
00:12:38,700 --> 00:12:40,530
[LUFFY]
Really? I'll do anything!

243
00:12:40,530 --> 00:12:44,290
Well then, I want you to come with me
to pay a little visit to Buggy the Pirate.

244
00:12:44,290 --> 00:12:45,200
But first...

245
00:12:49,290 --> 00:12:50,500
Why did you have to tie me up?

246
00:12:50,500 --> 00:12:52,790
The rope's just for appearances.

247
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:54,300
[LUFFY chuckles]
Well, okay then...

248
00:12:54,300 --> 00:12:57,670
I've been looking forward to meeting
some other pirates, so let's get going.

249
00:12:57,670 --> 00:13:00,130
Just hold your horses!
What's the big rush?

250
00:13:00,130 --> 00:13:02,930
[BUGGY]
What?!

251
00:13:02,930 --> 00:13:04,970
Are you telling me
the thief got away?!

252
00:13:05,180 --> 00:13:06,600
[HENCHMEN whimpering]

253
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,730
[ALL]
Please forgive us, Captain Buggy!

254
00:13:08,730 --> 00:13:11,980
I've never seen a more
pathetic group than you three!

255
00:13:11,980 --> 00:13:13,110
Time to die!

256
00:13:13,180 --> 00:13:14,260
[ALL scream]

257
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:16,480
Captain Buggy, I have news!

258
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,860
[BUGGY]
Ugh. What is it?!

259
00:13:17,860 --> 00:13:20,610
The girl who stole our chart is back,
and with a prisoner.

260
00:13:20,610 --> 00:13:21,570
[BUGGY]
What?!

261
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:24,660
[HENCHMAN X]
It's her!

262
00:13:24,660 --> 00:13:27,870
That's the sneaky thief
who stole the chart!

263
00:13:32,370 --> 00:13:35,380
[NAMI]
I've captured the thief,
Captain Buggy the Clown.

264
00:13:35,380 --> 00:13:37,340
And here's your chart back!

265
00:13:37,340 --> 00:13:39,510
Not that I don't appreciate it.

266
00:13:39,510 --> 00:13:42,300
But... why the sudden
change of heart, little girl?

267
00:13:44,760 --> 00:13:48,810
I had another fight with my boss,
and I just can't take it anymore!

268
00:13:48,810 --> 00:13:51,140
So I thought I'd see
if I could join your crew!

269
00:13:59,070 --> 00:14:00,440
You're fed up, huh?

270
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:02,450
I must admit, you're an amusing girl.

271
00:14:02,450 --> 00:14:04,870
I like you! Of course
you can join my crew!

272
00:14:09,870 --> 00:14:11,910
[NAMI]
I've successfully infiltrated them!

273
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:14,120
Pirates are so dumb
and easy to manipulate!

274
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:17,960
Hey, guys, why am I in a cage?

275
00:14:20,460 --> 00:14:22,550
It's a great day to be a pirate.

276
00:14:22,550 --> 00:14:24,800
Girl, what do you call yourself?

277
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:26,180
I'm Nami.

278
00:14:26,180 --> 00:14:27,300
Ha-ha!

279
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:30,060
Then let's have a welcome party
for our new friend Nami.

280
00:14:30,060 --> 00:14:31,180
Let's celebrate!

281
00:14:31,220 --> 00:14:36,310
[HENCHMEN cheering]

282
00:14:36,310 --> 00:14:45,230
[HENCHMEN chattering]

283
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,240
What's wrong?

284
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:53,120
We're throwing this party
in your honor, so eat up.

285
00:14:54,210 --> 00:14:56,040
Thanks for the party, Captain Buggy.

286
00:14:57,170 --> 00:15:01,090
[NAMI]
I'll just keep my eyes peeled
for a chance to take back that chart.

287
00:15:01,090 --> 00:15:04,720
Maybe I'll swipe all of Buggy's
treasure, too, while I'm at it.

288
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:08,640
Dammit!

289
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:20,070
This is such a flashy party.

290
00:15:20,070 --> 00:15:21,150
Now listen up!

291
00:15:22,570 --> 00:15:25,240
Men, it's time
to prepare the Buggy Ball!

292
00:15:43,210 --> 00:15:44,720
[HENCHMAN X]
All set, captain.

293
00:15:45,380 --> 00:15:47,970
Wh-What are you
doing with that thing?

294
00:15:47,970 --> 00:15:50,970
Just observe... the awesome
might of the Buggy Ball.

295
00:15:50,970 --> 00:15:51,720
Light it.

296
00:16:13,450 --> 00:16:15,290
That was one heck of an explosion.

297
00:16:15,290 --> 00:16:18,710
It looked like it was one of
the Captain's beloved Buggy Balls.

298
00:16:19,330 --> 00:16:20,750
Buggy Balls?

299
00:16:33,100 --> 00:16:34,140
That was flashy.

300
00:16:34,140 --> 00:16:36,770
With these Buggy Balls
and my devil fruit powers,

301
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:39,850
I should have no problem
conquering the Grand Line.

302
00:16:39,850 --> 00:16:41,060
Right, Nami?

303
00:16:41,060 --> 00:16:42,980
Right! Yes, of course!

304
00:16:42,980 --> 00:16:43,980
[LUFFY]
Huh?

305
00:16:43,980 --> 00:16:45,280
– [NAMI gasps]
– [BUGGY] Huh?

306
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:48,240
But it's my destiny to
conquer the Grand Line.

307
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:50,160
[growls]

308
00:16:50,160 --> 00:16:52,570
And then I'm gonna become
King of the Pirates!

309
00:16:52,570 --> 00:16:54,540
Shut up, idiot!

310
00:16:57,250 --> 00:16:59,870
[BUGGY]
I can see why
you're sick of him, Nami.

311
00:16:59,870 --> 00:17:01,170
Yeah, I know.

312
00:17:01,170 --> 00:17:04,550
He never takes anything seriously,
thinks that life's a big game.

313
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:06,760
He acts like a little kid.

314
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:08,840
– [NAMI laughs]
– [BUGGY] I see...

315
00:17:08,840 --> 00:17:13,300
[BUGGY]
Then how about I give you a Buggy
Ball to blow away your old boss?

316
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,300
Huh?

317
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:19,770
It'll be a great opportunity for you to prove
your loyalty to me, your new captain.

318
00:17:19,770 --> 00:17:20,440
Men!

319
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:31,200
That's all right Captain, we don't have to finish him off quite yet.

320
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:34,280
Let's get back to the welcoming
party and just have more fun.

321
00:17:36,290 --> 00:17:38,700
This is my idea of having more fun.

322
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:44,750
[HENCHMEN]
– Fire! Fire! Fire!
– Fire! Fire! Fire!

323
00:17:44,750 --> 00:17:48,630
Fire! Fire! Fire! Fire!

324
00:17:48,630 --> 00:17:56,310
Fire! Fire! Fire! Fire! Fire! Fire!

325
00:17:47,050 --> 00:17:49,840
[NAMI]
If I don't shoot, I'll be killed.

326
00:17:50,630 --> 00:17:54,680
But if I do shoot, then
I'm no better than these pirates...

327
00:17:56,810 --> 00:17:57,560
Now!

328
00:17:57,560 --> 00:17:58,970
Light the fuse, Nami!

329
00:18:00,390 --> 00:18:01,600
Fire

330
00:18:01,600 --> 00:18:06,690
More fire

331
00:18:06,690 --> 00:18:15,620
omg more fire

332
00:18:16,780 --> 00:18:17,780
[LUFFY]
What's the matter?

333
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:19,580
Your hands are shaking.

334
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,200
[LUFFY]
That's what happens

335
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:25,660
when you take on pirates
with half‐assed resolve.

336
00:18:26,340 --> 00:18:28,250
To kill someone
like it's nothing?

337
00:18:28,250 --> 00:18:29,920
Is that a pirate's resolve?

338
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:31,590
[LUFFY]
No!

339
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:38,170
You gotta be willing
to risk your own life.

340
00:18:38,170 --> 00:18:41,010
[HENCHMEN]
Fire! Fire! Fire!

341
00:18:41,010 --> 00:18:43,850
Fire! Fire! Fire!

342
00:18:43,850 --> 00:18:44,850
[NAMI gasps]

343
00:18:44,190 --> 00:18:45,350
Here, new chick.

344
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:46,980
Quit bein' sucha tease.

345
00:18:46,980 --> 00:18:49,190
Let me show you how
to light the cannon.

346
00:18:59,660 --> 00:19:01,030
My mistake... Sorry.

347
00:19:01,030 --> 00:19:02,450
[BUGGY growls]

348
00:19:02,620 --> 00:19:03,450
Nami!

349
00:19:03,450 --> 00:19:05,790
What's the meaning
of this outrage?!

350
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:07,130
[NAMI]
I'm sorry.

351
00:19:07,130 --> 00:19:09,880
What's wrong?! Just
shoot him already!

352
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:11,230
[HENCHMAN X chuckles]

353
00:19:11,230 --> 00:19:13,570
Hey, wake up little girl.

354
00:19:13,570 --> 00:19:16,130
[GIRL]
Uh.

355
00:19:16,130 --> 00:19:18,740
Please tell me I'm not
dreaming this time...

356
00:19:18,740 --> 00:19:21,910
finding help out here
in the middle of nowhere...

357
00:19:21,910 --> 00:19:24,940
If you're real, then please,
could you get me some water?

358
00:19:24,940 --> 00:19:27,610
I'm so thirsty.

359
00:19:27,610 --> 00:19:30,080
I'll give you as much jewelry
and valuables as you like,

360
00:19:23,100 --> 00:19:25,430
Pirates took the life of
a person very dear to me.

361
00:19:25,430 --> 00:19:27,310
I'll never be one of them.

362
00:19:27,310 --> 00:19:29,270
Oh, I see.

363
00:19:29,270 --> 00:19:31,980
[LUFFY yelps]

364
00:19:31,980 --> 00:19:33,270
Nami! The fuse!

365
00:19:33,270 --> 00:19:34,190
[gasps]

366
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:31,770
Nami! The fuse!

367
00:19:31,770 --> 00:19:32,690
[gasps]

368
00:19:34,150 --> 00:19:36,230
So you think pirates
are just inhuman filth,

369
00:19:36,230 --> 00:19:37,310
is that right?

370
00:19:37,310 --> 00:19:38,860
Get her, men!

371
00:19:38,860 --> 00:19:40,740
[HENCHMEN yelling]

372
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:48,330
Flashy... death...
awaits... them...

373
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:51,380
Water, water,
water, water, water!

374
00:19:56,590 --> 00:19:57,720
[NAMI grunts]

375
00:20:04,930 --> 00:20:05,980
Whoa!

376
00:20:11,270 --> 00:20:12,230
Watch out!

377
00:20:12,230 --> 00:20:14,320
– [HENCHMEN yelling]
– [NAMI gasps]

378
00:20:20,620 --> 00:20:22,080
[ZORO]
Hey now.

379
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:26,580
[laughs]

380
00:20:28,080 --> 00:20:29,080
Zoro!

381
00:20:29,080 --> 00:20:30,080
[NAMI]
Huh?

382
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:35,880
[ZORO]
You hurt?

383
00:20:36,670 --> 00:20:39,290
[NAMI]
Uh, no, I'm fine, I think.

384
00:20:39,290 --> 00:20:41,380
[LUFFY]
Whew, what a relief!

385
00:20:41,380 --> 00:20:42,710
I'm glad you found us.

386
00:20:42,710 --> 00:20:44,800
Now hurry up and come
get me out of here.

387
00:20:44,800 --> 00:20:47,130
[ZORO] How do keep getting
yourself into these situations?

388
00:20:47,130 --> 00:20:48,390
First a bird flies off with you,

389
00:20:48,390 --> 00:20:50,680
and now I find you
trapped in a cage.

390
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:53,680
[LUFFY] It's an
interesting story, actually.

391
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:54,680
That's...

392
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:58,150
Yeah... That little brat
just called him Zoro.

393
00:20:58,150 --> 00:21:00,480
[NAMI]
The crew he mentioned earlier...

394
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:03,480
was the Pirate Hunter Zoro?

395
00:20:56,110 --> 00:20:57,900
[LUFFY]
Hm?

396
00:20:57,900 --> 00:21:00,570
[ZORO]
Hey, look, a bird.

397
00:21:00,990 --> 00:21:03,320
[NAMI]
The crew he mentioned earlier...

398
00:21:03,320 --> 00:21:06,320
was the Pirate Hunter Zoro?

399
00:21:06,080 --> 00:21:07,750
What's going on here?

400
00:21:09,080 --> 00:21:10,290
[BUGGY]
So you're Zoro?

401
00:21:10,290 --> 00:21:11,450
[NAMI gasps]

402
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:12,950
[BUGGY]
If you're here for my head,

403
00:21:12,950 --> 00:21:15,830
you've got quite a
struggle before you.

404
00:21:15,840 --> 00:21:17,840
Now I'm really pissed off!

405
00:21:17,840 --> 00:21:20,930
Alright, Prepare all the
remaining Special Buggy Balls.

406
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:23,550
But I'm interested, though.

407
00:21:23,550 --> 00:21:26,720
Killing you would
bolster my reputation.

408
00:21:26,810 --> 00:21:27,970
If you try...

409
00:21:27,970 --> 00:21:29,430
you'll die.

410
00:21:29,430 --> 00:21:31,600
Oh. Is that so?

411
00:21:33,980 --> 00:21:36,230
I tried to warn you,
but oh well...

412
00:21:36,900 --> 00:21:38,270
[HENCHMAN X]
You can do it, Buggy!

413
00:21:38,270 --> 00:21:39,560
[HENCHMEN cheering]

414
00:21:39,560 --> 00:21:42,570
[HENCHMEN]
Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!

415
00:21:42,570 --> 00:21:45,900
Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!

416
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:51,580
Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!

417
00:21:51,580 --> 00:21:54,330
[snickers]

418
00:21:54,330 --> 00:22:02,340
[BUGGY yelling, laughing]

419
00:22:02,340 --> 00:22:05,470
[BUGGY]
Die flashily!

420
00:21:56,170 --> 00:21:59,340
If you'll accept, I'll
even pay you to stop this.

421
00:22:13,560 --> 00:22:15,860
That wasn't much of
a fight, now was it?

422
00:22:15,860 --> 00:22:17,480
Oh, wow!

423
00:22:17,480 --> 00:22:19,280
He's weak! Way to go, Zoro!

424
00:22:19,780 --> 00:22:20,860
He's weak! Way to go, Zoro!

425
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,740
Hey, why are they laughing?

426
00:22:32,740 --> 00:22:34,620
Their captain is lying
dead on the ground

427
00:22:34,620 --> 00:22:36,370
and yet they're still laughing?

428
00:22:36,370 --> 00:22:37,410
What's going on?

429
00:22:37,410 --> 00:22:38,620
[ZORO]
Fellas.

430
00:22:38,620 --> 00:22:41,460
What do you find so damn funny?

431
00:22:41,460 --> 00:22:43,580
– [thud]
– [ZORO grunts]

432
00:22:43,580 --> 00:22:46,090
[ZORO groans]

433
00:22:46,090 --> 00:22:49,090
[ZORO screams]

434
00:22:49,060 --> 00:22:50,520
[ZORO screams]

435
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:53,640
[LUFFY]
Stupid, stupid, stupid, dog!

436
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:55,760
Give it back. That's not food!

437
00:22:55,760 --> 00:22:56,970
Give me my key!

438
00:22:56,970 --> 00:23:00,640
Give it, give it, give it, give
it, give it, give it, give it!

439
00:22:59,110 --> 00:23:01,030
[ZORO gasps]

440
00:23:02,110 --> 00:23:05,360
[BUGGY]
The Chop‐Chop Fruit.

441
00:23:06,870 --> 00:23:10,870
I'm a Chop‐Chop person,

442
00:23:13,710 --> 00:23:16,420
[laughing]

443
00:23:16,420 --> 00:23:18,590
His limbs... reattach?

444
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:20,920
And I always thought that the
devil fruits were just a story

445
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,210
that Pirates told.

446
00:23:22,210 --> 00:23:23,920
So he's a Chop‐Chop man?

447
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:25,590
That's pretty freaky.

448
00:23:25,930 --> 00:23:29,600
I didn't hit any vital organs,

449
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:30,640
but that's a serious
wound you have there.

450
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:36,600
So I'm guessing...

451
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:32,640
but that's a serious
wound you have there.

452
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:33,810
So I'm guessing...

453
00:23:33,890 --> 00:23:36,600
Buggy Balls?

454
00:23:37,440 --> 00:23:39,270
[NAMI]
Oh, crap!

455
00:23:39,270 --> 00:23:41,270
The tables have turned.

456
00:23:41,270 --> 00:23:42,820
If we don't do something quick,

457
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:49,160
[groaning]

458
00:23:54,620 --> 00:23:57,620
[HENCHMEN]
Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!

459
00:23:57,620 --> 00:24:00,960
Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!

460
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:06,630
Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!

461
00:24:06,630 --> 00:24:09,380
[snickers]

462
00:24:09,380 --> 00:24:17,390
[BUGGY yelling, laughing]

463
00:24:17,390 --> 00:24:20,520
[BUGGY]
Die flashily!

464
00:24:20,520 --> 00:24:24,230
[NAMI whimpers]

465
00:24:24,230 --> 00:24:26,520
[HENCHMEN gasp]

466
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:07,470
Shut up, idiot!

467
00:24:07,470 --> 00:24:10,510
[laughing]

468
00:24:10,510 --> 00:24:12,800
[BUGGY] I can see why
you're sick of him, Nami.

469
00:24:12,350 --> 00:24:13,810
What's that...

470
00:24:13,810 --> 00:24:14,810
you...

471
00:24:19,190 --> 00:24:19,850
[HENCHMAN X] So, any ideas
about what we do now?

472
00:24:21,690 --> 00:24:22,820
Luffy!

473
00:24:24,230 --> 00:24:27,280
I'm here to kick your ass, just
like I promised I would, Buggy!

474
00:24:31,530 --> 00:24:34,360
[BUGGY laughing]

475
00:24:34,360 --> 00:24:36,070
You kick my ass?

476
00:24:36,070 --> 00:24:37,740
You've got a lot of nerve, kid.

477
00:24:37,740 --> 00:24:39,200
No, I'm afraid all three of you

478
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:42,740
are going to die here
today, by my own hand.

479
00:24:38,420 --> 00:24:41,960
are going to die here
today, by my own hand.

480
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:44,420
So if you're going to
do any ass kicking,

481
00:24:44,420 --> 00:24:45,960
you better do it soon.

482
00:24:45,960 --> 00:24:47,670
[BUGGY laughing]

483
00:24:47,670 --> 00:24:49,470
[NAMI gasps]

484
00:24:47,630 --> 00:24:50,590
[NAMI gasps]

485
00:24:53,260 --> 00:24:55,220
[LUFFY laughing]

486
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:57,310
[LUFFY]
I refuse to die!

487
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:58,310
Zoro! Get up!

488
00:24:58,310 --> 00:25:01,560
What?!

489
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:03,060
You better have a really good
plan or else we're all dead.

490
00:25:08,990 --> 00:25:09,990
I gotcha.

491
00:25:10,240 --> 00:25:13,140
[ZORO] You're a rubber guy.
How human do you think that is?

492
00:25:13,140 --> 00:25:14,810
[GIRL]
Nothing makes sense anymore.

493
00:25:14,810 --> 00:25:15,740
A rubber guy,

494
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:17,580
This is why I hate pirates.

495
00:25:17,580 --> 00:25:21,250
[BUGGY]
Impudent fool! Time to die!

496
00:25:21,250 --> 00:25:30,550
[BUGGY] Your Three‐Sword
Style has no effect on me.

497
00:25:25,750 --> 00:25:28,480
[GIRL panting]

498
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:30,420
[GIRL]
Yes, I've finally got it!

499
00:25:30,420 --> 00:25:32,350
Hey girl, get back here!

500
00:25:30,930 --> 00:25:33,390
I already told you I'm‐‐

501
00:25:50,450 --> 00:25:53,410
– [BUGGY screams]
– [HENCHMEN gasp]

502
00:25:53,870 --> 00:25:54,990
Light it.

503
00:25:54,990 --> 00:26:06,210
[chuckles]

504
00:26:06,210 --> 00:26:14,680
[yelps]

